latestPosts.caption:
Vintage Kitchen (Since 2017) @vintagekitchenklson 
“Fueling your day with freshness and flavour, the healthy home way”
Found this beautiful little café while strolling around in the lanes of U-Block with my friend😍
Vintage Kitchen has a small seating area with comfortable and cosy furniture, pleasing ambience, decent decor and a small kitchen spreading the flavoursome smell of the food being cooked.  The service is quick and the manager is genuine enough to personally collect your feedback and most importantly value your opinion. The presentation of the food is done right and the portion of food served won’t disappoint you. Lots of lights are going to catch your attention though❤️
Ps.. Mobile free dining offer..(5% for solo and 10% for group) T&C*
@meta @metaindia @meta.ai 

Must visited place.. with family/friends ❤️

Location- U-14a/1, Galli No 14a, U Block, DLF Phase 3, Sector 24, Gurugram, Haryana 122003
